  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "NEgpGdvgRAjWDYI8q+fSNuZu1Cg=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:27.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "The Bee Reactor Adapter delivers decentralized storage and encrypted chat for [Powerhouse Connect](https://powerhouse.io) on the [Swarm](https://ethswarm.org) network, eliminating the need for centralized servers.\n\nCore capabilities:\n- Encrypt documents with the user's Ethereum wallet\n- Store encrypted data on Swarm\n- Recover on any device using just a wallet signature\n- Share drives with other users\n- Chat directly peer-to-peer via PSS + GSOC\n\nThe adapter integrates as a native reactor `IChannel` via `createSwarmSyncBuilder()`. The Connect fork wires it into `ReactorBuilder.withSync()` at build time, so Swarm remotes persist in `sync_remotes` and survive page reloads natively alongside GQL channels. The landing page forces wallet login, the plugin syncs all drives and docs to Swarm automatically, and exposes a chat panel from the sidebar.",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:27.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:27.000Z"
    }
  },
